#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:5
msgid "Layout Items Common Options"
msgstr "Zajedničke opcije stavki rasporeda"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:12
msgid ""
"QGIS provides a large set of items to layout a map. They can be of map, "
"legend, scale bar, picture, table, north arrow, image type... They however "
"share some common options and behavior that are exposed below."
msgstr ""
"QGIS pruža veliki skup stavki za raspoređivanje karte. Mogu biti tipa karte,"
" legende, razmernika, slike, tabele, strelice severa, slike... Međutim, dele"
" neke zajedničke opcije i ponašanje koji su izloženi ispod."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:19
msgid "Creating a layout item"
msgstr "Pravljenje stavke rasporeda"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:21
msgid ""
"Items can be created using different tools, either from scratch or based on "
"existing items."
msgstr ""
"Stavke se mogu praviti pomoću različitih alatki, bilo od nule ili na osnovu "
"postojećih stavki."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:23
msgid "To create a layout item from scratch:"
msgstr "Da biste napravili stavku rasporeda od nule:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:25
msgid ""
"Select the corresponding tool either from the :menuselection:`Add Item` menu"
" or the :guilabel:`Toolbox` bar."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite odgovarajuću alatku iz menija :menuselection:`Dodaj stavku` ili "
"trake :guilabel:`Kutija sa alatkama`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:27
msgid "Then:"
msgstr "Zatim:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click on the page and fill the size and placement information requested in "
"the :guilabel:`New Item Properties` dialog that pops up (for details, see "
":ref:`position_size`);"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na stranu i popunite informacije o veličini i položaju zatražene u "
"dijalogu :guilabel:`Svojstva nove stavke` koji iskoči (za detalje pogledajte"
" :ref:`position_size`);"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:38
msgid "New Item properties dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog Svojstva nove stavke"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:40
msgid ""
"Or click-and-drag to define the initial size and placement of the item. You "
"can rely on :ref:`grids and guides <grid_guides>` snapping for a better "
"position."
msgstr ""
"Ili kliknite i prevucite da biste definisali početnu veličinu i položaj "
"stavke. Za bolji položaj možete se osloniti na lepljenje za :ref:`mreže i "
"vodilje <grid_guides>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:44
msgid ""
"Because they can have particular shapes, drawing node or arrow items does "
"not work with one-click nor click-and-drag methods; you need to click and "
"place each node of the item. See :ref:`layout_node_based_shape_item` for "
"more details."
msgstr ""
"Pošto mogu imati posebne oblike, crtanje stavki sa čvorovima ili strelica ne"
" radi metodima jednog klika ni klika i prevlačenja; potrebno je da kliknete "
"i postavite svaki čvor stavke. Za više detalja pogledajte "
":ref:`layout_node_based_shape_item`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:49
msgid "You can also:"
msgstr "Takođe možete:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:51
msgid ""
"Select an existing item with the |select| :sup:`Select/Move item` button "
"from the :guilabel:`Toolbox` toolbar"
msgstr ""
"Izabrati postojeću stavku dugmetom |select| :sup:`Izaberi/pomeri stavku` iz "
"palete alatki :guilabel:`Kutija sa alatkama`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:361
msgid "select"
msgstr "select"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:53
msgid ""
"Use the contextual menu or the :menuselection:`Edit` menu tools to copy/cut "
"the item and paste it at the mouse position as a new item."
msgstr ""
"Koristiti kontekstni meni ili alatke menija :menuselection:`Uređivanje` da "
"biste kopirali/isekli stavku i nalepili je na položaj miša kao novu stavku."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:56
msgid ""
"You can also use the :guilabel:`Paste in Place` (:kbd:`Ctrl+Shift+V`) "
"command to duplicate an item from one page to another and place it in the "
"new page at the same coordinates as the original."
msgstr ""
"Takođe možete koristiti komandu :guilabel:`Nalepi na mesto` "
"(:kbd:`Ctrl+Shift+V`) da biste duplirali stavku sa jedne strane na drugu i "
"postavili je na novu stranu na istim koordinatama kao original."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:60
msgid ""
"Moreover, you can create items using a print layout template (for details, "
"see :ref:`layout_manager`) through the :menuselection:`Layout --> Add Items "
"from Template...` command."
msgstr ""
"Osim toga, stavke možete praviti pomoću šablona rasporeda za štampu (za "
"detalje pogledajte :ref:`layout_manager`) komandom :menuselection:`Raspored "
"--> Dodaj stavke iz šablona...`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:63
msgid "**Add layout items using the file browser**"
msgstr "**Dodavanje stavki rasporeda pomoću pregledača datoteka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:65
msgid ""
"From your file browser or using the :guilabel:`Browser` panel, drag-and-drop"
" a print layout template (:file:`.qpt` file) onto a print layout dialog and "
"QGIS automatically adds all items from that template to the layout."
msgstr ""
"Iz svog pregledača datoteka ili pomoću panela :guilabel:`Pregledač`, "
"prevucite šablon rasporeda za štampu (:file:`.qpt` datoteku) na dijalog "
"rasporeda za štampu, a QGIS automatski dodaje sve stavke iz tog šablona u "
"raspored."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:72
msgid "Interacting with layout items"
msgstr "Interakcija sa stavkama rasporeda"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:73
msgid ""
"Each item inside the print layout can be moved and resized to create a "
"perfect layout. For both operations the first step is to activate the "
"|select| :sup:`Select/Move item` tool and click on the item."
msgstr ""
"Svaka stavka unutar rasporeda za štampu može se pomeriti i promeniti "
"veličina radi pravljenja savršenog rasporeda. Za obe operacije prvi korak je"
" aktiviranje alatke |select| :sup:`Izaberi/pomeri stavku` i klik na stavku."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:77
msgid ""
"You can select multiple items with the |select| :sup:`Select/Move item` "
"button: click and drag over the items or hold the :kbd:`Shift` button and "
"click on each of the items you want. To deselect an item, click on it "
"holding the :kbd:`Shift` button."
msgstr ""
"Možete izabrati više stavki dugmetom |select| :sup:`Izaberi/pomeri stavku`: "
"kliknite i prevucite preko stavki ili držite dugme :kbd:`Shift` i kliknite "
"na svaku od stavki koje želite. Da biste poništili izbor stavke, kliknite na"
" nju držeći dugme :kbd:`Shift`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:82
msgid ""
"Each time there's a selection, count of selected items is displayed on the "
"status bar. Inside the :menuselection:`Edit` menu, you can find actions to "
"select all the items, clear all selections, invert the current selection and"
" more..."
msgstr ""
"Svaki put kada postoji izbor, broj izabranih stavki prikazuje se u statusnoj"
" traci. Unutar menija :menuselection:`Uređivanje` možete pronaći radnje za "
"izbor svih stavki, poništavanje svih izbora, obrtanje trenutnog izbora i još"
" mnogo toga..."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:89
msgid "Moving and resizing items"
msgstr "Pomeranje i promena veličine stavki"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:91
msgid ""
"Unless :menuselection:`View --> Show Bounding Boxes` option is unchecked, a "
"selected item will show squares on its boundaries; moving one of them with "
"the mouse will resize the item in the corresponding direction. While "
"resizing, holding :kbd:`Shift` will maintain the aspect ratio. Holding "
":kbd:`Alt` will resize from the item center."
msgstr ""
"Osim ako je opcija :menuselection:`Prikaz --> Prikaži granične "
"pravougaonike` poništena, izabrana stavka će prikazati kvadratiće na svojim "
"granicama; pomeranje jednog od njih mišem promeniće veličinu stavke u "
"odgovarajućem pravcu. Tokom promene veličine, držanje :kbd:`Shift` održaće "
"odnos stranica. Držanje :kbd:`Alt` će promeniti veličinu iz centra stavke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:97
msgid ""
"To move a layout item, select it with the mouse and move while holding the "
"left button. If you need to constrain the movements to the horizontal or "
"vertical axis, hold the :kbd:`Shift` button on the keyboard while moving the"
" mouse. You can also move a selected item using the :kbd:`Arrow keys` on the"
" keyboard; if the movement is too slow, you can speed it up by holding "
":kbd:`Shift`. If you need better precision, use the :guilabel:`Position and "
"size` properties, or grid/guides snapping as explained above for item's "
"creation."
msgstr ""
"Da biste pomerili stavku rasporeda, izaberite je mišem i pomerajte držeći "
"levi taster. Ako je potrebno da ograničite kretanje na horizontalnu ili "
"vertikalnu osu, držite dugme :kbd:`Shift` na tastaturi dok pomerate miša. "
"Izabranu stavku možete pomeriti i pomoću :kbd:`Arrow keys` na tastaturi; ako"
" je kretanje presporo, možete ga ubrzati držanjem :kbd:`Shift`. Ako vam je "
"potrebna veća preciznost, koristite svojstva :guilabel:`Položaj i veličina`,"
" ili lepljenje za mrežu/vodilje kako je objašnjeno gore za pravljenje "
"stavke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:105
msgid ""
"Resizing or moving several items at once is made the same way as for a "
"single item. QGIS however provides some advanced tools to automatically "
"resize a selection of items following different rules:"
msgstr ""
"Promena veličine ili pomeranje više stavki odjednom vrši se na isti način "
"kao za jednu stavku. QGIS, međutim, pruža neke napredne alatke za automatsku"
" promenu veličine izbora stavki prema različitim pravilima:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:109
msgid ""
"each item height matches the |resizeTallest| tallest or the |resizeShortest|"
" shortest selected item;"
msgstr ""
"visina svake stavke odgovara |resizeTallest| najvišoj ili |resizeShortest| "
"najnižoj izabranoj stavki;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:357
msgid "resizeTallest"
msgstr "resizeTallest"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:353
msgid "resizeShortest"
msgstr "resizeShortest"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:110
msgid ""
"each item width matches the |resizeWidest| widest or the |resizeNarrowest| "
"narrowest selected item;"
msgstr ""
"širina svake stavke odgovara |resizeWidest| najširoj ili |resizeNarrowest| "
"najužoj izabranoj stavki;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:359
msgid "resizeWidest"
msgstr "resizeWidest"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:351
msgid "resizeNarrowest"
msgstr "resizeNarrowest"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:111
msgid ""
"resizes items to |resizeSquare| squares: each item is enlarged to shape a "
"square."
msgstr ""
"menja veličinu stavki na |resizeSquare| kvadrate: svaka stavka se uvećava da"
" bi dobila oblik kvadrata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:355
msgid "resizeSquare"
msgstr "resizeSquare"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:113
msgid ""
"Likewise, there are :ref:`tools <align_items>` available to organize "
"multiple items position by distributing equidistantly:"
msgstr ""
"Isto tako, dostupne su :ref:`alatke <align_items>` za organizovanje položaja"
" više stavki jednakim rasporedom:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:116
msgid "edges (left, right, top or bottom) of items;"
msgstr "ivica (leve, desne, gornje ili donje) stavki;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:117
msgid "centers of items horizontally or vertically;"
msgstr "centara stavki horizontalno ili vertikalno;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:118
msgid "spacing between items horizontally or vertically."
msgstr "razmaka između stavki horizontalno ili vertikalno."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:123
msgid "Grouping items"
msgstr "Grupisanje stavki"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:125
msgid ""
"Grouping items allows you to manipulate a set of items like a single one: "
"you can easily resize, move, delete, copy the items as a whole."
msgstr ""
"Grupisanje stavki omogućava vam da manipulišete skupom stavki kao jednom: "
"možete lako promeniti veličinu, pomeriti, obrisati, kopirati stavke kao "
"celinu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:128
msgid ""
"To create a group of items, select more than one and press the |groupItems| "
":guilabel:`Group` button on the :menuselection:`Items` menu or the "
":guilabel:`Actions` toolbar, or from the right-click menu. A row named "
"``Group`` is added to the :menuselection:`Items` panel and can be locked or "
"hidden like any other :ref:`Items panel's object <layout_items_panel>`. "
"Grouped items are **not individually** selectable on the canvas; use the "
"Items panel for direct selection and access the item's properties panel."
msgstr ""
"Da biste napravili grupu stavki, izaberite više od jedne i pritisnite dugme "
"|groupItems| :guilabel:`Grupiši` u meniju :menuselection:`Stavke` ili paleti"
" alatki :guilabel:`Radnje`, ili iz menija desnog klika. Red pod nazivom "
"``Group`` se dodaje u panel :menuselection:`Stavke` i može se zaključati ili"
" sakriti kao bilo koji drugi :ref:`objekat panela Stavke "
"<layout_items_panel>`. Grupisane stavke **nisu pojedinačno** izborljive na "
"platnu; koristite panel Stavke za direktan izbor i pristup panelu svojstava "
"stavke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:343
msgid "groupItems"
msgstr "groupItems"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:138
msgid "Locking items"
msgstr "Zaključavanje stavki"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:140
msgid ""
"Once you have found the correct position for an item, you can lock it by "
"using the |locked| :guilabel:`Lock selected items` button in the "
":menuselection:`Items` menu or the :guilabel:`Actions` toolbar, or ticking "
"the box next to the item in the :menuselection:`Items` panel. Locked items "
"are **not** selectable on the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Kada pronađete ispravan položaj za stavku, možete je zaključati pomoću "
"dugmeta |locked| :guilabel:`Zaključaj izabrane stavke` u meniju "
":menuselection:`Stavke` ili paleti alatki :guilabel:`Radnje`, ili "
"označavanjem polja pored stavke u panelu :menuselection:`Stavke`. Zaključane"
" stavke **nisu** izborljive na platnu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:345
msgid "locked"
msgstr "locked"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:145
msgid ""
"Locked items can be unlocked by selecting the item in the "
":menuselection:`Items` panel and unchecking the tickbox or you can use the "
"icons on the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Zaključane stavke mogu se otključati izborom stavke u panelu "
":menuselection:`Stavke` i poništavanjem polja ili možete koristiti ikone u "
"paleti alatki."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:152
msgid "Alignment and distribution"
msgstr "Poravnanje i raspoređivanje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:154
msgid ""
"Tools for raising or lowering the Z position of items in the layout are "
"inside the |raiseItems| :sup:`Raise selected items` pull-down menu. Choose "
"an element on the print layout canvas and select the matching functionality "
"to raise or lower the selected element over the other elements. This order "
"is shown in the :menuselection:`Items` panel. You can also raise or lower "
"objects in the :menuselection:`Items` panel by clicking and dragging an "
"object's label in this list."
msgstr ""
"Alatke za podizanje ili spuštanje Z položaja stavki u rasporedu nalaze se u "
"padajućem meniju |raiseItems| :sup:`Podigni izabrane stavke`. Izaberite "
"element na platnu rasporeda za štampu i izaberite odgovarajuću "
"funkcionalnost za podizanje ili spuštanje izabranog elementa iznad drugih "
"elemenata. Ovaj redosled se prikazuje u panelu :menuselection:`Stavke`. "
"Objekte možete podizati ili spuštati i u panelu :menuselection:`Stavke` "
"klikom i prevlačenjem natpisa objekta u ovoj listi."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:349
msgid "raiseItems"
msgstr "raiseItems"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:167
msgid "Alignment helper lines in the print layout"
msgstr "Pomoćne linije poravnanja u rasporedu za štampu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:169
msgid ""
"There are several alignment options available within the |alignLeft| "
":sup:`Align selected items` pull-down menu (see "
":numref:`figure_layout_common_align`). To use an alignment function, you "
"first select the elements and then click on one of the alignment icons:"
msgstr ""
"U padajućem meniju |alignLeft| :sup:`Poravnaj izabrane stavke` dostupno je "
"nekoliko opcija poravnanja (pogledajte "
":numref:`figure_layout_common_align`). Da biste koristili funkciju "
"poravnanja, prvo izaberite elemente, a zatim kliknite na jednu od ikona "
"poravnanja:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:315
msgid "alignLeft"
msgstr "alignLeft"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:174
msgid ""
"|alignLeft| :guilabel:`Align Left` or |alignRight| :guilabel:`Align Right`;"
msgstr ""
"|alignLeft| :guilabel:`Poravnaj levo` ili |alignRight| :guilabel:`Poravnaj "
"desno`;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:317
msgid "alignRight"
msgstr "alignRight"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:175
msgid ""
"|alignTop| :guilabel:`Align Top` or |alignBottom| :guilabel:`Align Bottom`;"
msgstr ""
"|alignTop| :guilabel:`Poravnaj gore` ili |alignBottom| :guilabel:`Poravnaj "
"dole`;"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:319
msgid "alignTop"
msgstr "alignTop"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:311
msgid "alignBottom"
msgstr "alignBottom"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:176
msgid ""
"|alignHCenter| :guilabel:`Align Center` horizontally or |alignVCenter| "
":guilabel:`Align Center Vertical`."
msgstr ""
"|alignHCenter| :guilabel:`Poravnaj po centru` horizontalno ili "
"|alignVCenter| :guilabel:`Poravnaj po centru vertikalno`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:313
msgid "alignHCenter"
msgstr "alignHCenter"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:321
msgid "alignVCenter"
msgstr "alignVCenter"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:178
msgid ""
"All selected elements will then be aligned to their common bounding box. "
"When moving items on the layout canvas, alignment helper lines appear when "
"borders, centers or corners are aligned."
msgstr ""
"Svi izabrani elementi biće tada poravnati prema svom zajedničkom graničnom "
"pravougaoniku. Pri pomeranju stavki na platnu rasporeda, pomoćne linije "
"poravnanja se pojavljuju kada su ivice, centri ili uglovi poravnati."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/print_layout/layout_items/layout_items_options.rst:181
msgid ""
"Another way to improve layout items placement is by adjusting the spacing "
"between them, over the layout page. This can be done by selecting the items "
"and press the |distributeLeft| :guilabel:`Distribute Left Edges` drop-down "
"menu to:"
msgstr ""
"Još jedan način poboljšanja položaja stavki rasporeda jeste prilagođavanje "
"razmaka između njih, preko strane rasporeda. To se može uraditi izborom "
"stavki i pritiskom na padajući meni |distributeLeft| :guilabel:`Rasporedi "
"leve ivice` da biste:"

